&trans     &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans              &mkp RCLK  &kp NUMBER_4  &kp NUMBER_5  &kp NUMBER_6  &kp ENTER  &trans   &trans      &kp PAGE_DOWN               &trans
&trans     &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans              &none      &kp NUMBER_1  &kp NUMBER_2  &kp NUMBER_3  &kp ENTER  &trans   &trans      &kp PG_DN                   &trans
